{"tid":1250183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淘寶購童裝T恤 收貨發覺多了句罵警粗口  「Fxxx the police」","createTime":"2019-06-22T03:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:08:04.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"960f4fe7d5938acacf2fae095c7aa69d34dac5fe","tid":1250183,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:43:44.000Z","msg":"潮流興網上購物，但當你收貨時，往往是驚嚇多於驚喜。 <br />\n<br />\n英國一位母親為她的3歲女兒在網上購買了一件T恤，但收貨時，竟發覺該件T恤原來是兒童不宜。 <br />\n<br />\n威廉遜太太(Kelsey Williamson)在廉價貨網站AliExpress見到一件印有「青蛙與蟾蜍」(Frog and Toad)的童裝T恤，沒有任何標誌或文字，只賣3鎊(約30港元)，覺得頗不錯，於是落單買給女兒薩琳(Salem)穿。據網上資料，AliExpress是中國阿里巴巴集團旗下購物網站。 <br />\n<br />\n但當她收貨時，不禁大嚇一跳，因為在「青蛙與蟾蜍」的公仔下，竟印著一句大大的粗口「Fxxx the police」。威廉遜太太與丈夫在苦笑下，不忘與網友分享其網購奇遇，於是讓女兒穿上T恤拍照放上Facebook的購物慘事群組，怎料惹起網民反彈。威廉遜太太唯有在照片下加句語：「薩琳只有3歲，未識字」、「我沒有買這件T恤，但收到的貨就是這樣。她不會公開穿，『為何我要拍照？』你都會吧，不要騙人了」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190621/large/1561076082_1b5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190621%2Flarge%2F1561076082_1b5d.jpg&h=bc03239f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190621/59740870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59740870&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2Bh8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=29c95a2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59740870&h=cc843ffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190621/59740870</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1259b58dd41536f11e0e1a705c92659c2bbc0e78","tid":1250183,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:45:04.000Z","msg":"AliExpress即係淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc71423450cbe147e62e67f0b0adfcedae7b8c2","tid":1250183,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"其他網民=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5717d9cfcbd68eaa052e577ee22a3383e95b5a","tid":1250183,"uid":27899,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dW59CqC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdW59CqC.png&h=2341176b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}